OL,3,CClosure on busy section of Metro as
OL,4,CShields Ferry remains out of action
OL,6,FA busy section of the Tyne and Wear
OL,7,FMetro line serving North Tyneside and
OL,8,FNewcastle is now closed to allow for
OL,9,Ftrack renewal works.
OL,11,FNo trains will run between Shiremoor
OL,12,Fand St James, in both directions, from
OL,13,FMonday (16 February) to Friday.
OL,15,FA replacement bus service is running
OL,16,Fduring the project, calling at or
OL,17,Fclose to all affected Metro stations,
OL,18,Fwith the affected route set to reopen
OL,19,Fon Saturday.
