OL,3,CClosure on busy section of Metro as
OL,4,CShields Ferry remains out of action
OL,6,FPaul Welford, Major Projects Director
OL,7,Fat Nexus, said: "We're investing in
OL,8,Fnew track and other key infrastructure
OL,9,Fto ensure that Metro continues to
OL,10,Freliably serve North Tyneside and
OL,11,FNewcastle for many years to come.
OL,13,F"There is no good time to close a
OL,14,Fsection of the network, and we do so
OL,15,Fto minimise disruption to as many
OL,16,Fcustomers as possible. Our plans
OL,17,Fconsider school holidays, to ensure
OL,18,Fthe least possible disruption to
OL,19,Fcustomers and the most efficient
OL,20,Fworks. "
