OL,3,CClosure on busy section of Metro as
OL,4,CShields Ferry remains out of action
OL,6,FThe major line closure comes as the
OL,7,FShields Ferry remains out of action
OL,8,Ffollowing storm damage to the North
OL,9,FShields landing.
OL,11,FThe service is suspended until the end
OL,12,Fof February while repairs take place
OL,13,Fand a replacement bus service is
OL,14,Frunning via the Tyne Tunnel.
OL,16,FDuring the programme of investment on
OL,17,Fthe Metro this week, on the yellow
OL,18,Fline, Metro services will run from
OL,19,FShiremoor towards South Shields via
OL,20,FSouth Gosforth calling at all stations
OL,21,Fon route.
