OL,3,CClosure on busy section of Metro as
OL,4,CShields Ferry remains out of action
OL,6,FThe green line will be unaffected by
OL,7,Fthe closure.
OL,9,FMetro operator Nexus said the work is
OL,10,Fpart of its Asset Renewal Programme `
OL,11,Fwhich involves the modernisation of
OL,12,Fkey items of Metro infrastructure,
OL,13,Fincluding tracks and overhead lines.
OL,15,FAs part of the renewal work, a total
OL,16,Fof 950 metres of new track will be
OL,17,Finstalled between Chillingham Road and
OL,18,FWalkergate, and more than 1,000
OL,19,Fsleepers are being replaced.
