OL,3,CClosure on busy section of Metro as
OL,4,CShields Ferry remains out of action
OL,6,FOther important works include cable
OL,7,Ftesting, lineside estate management,
OL,8,Fplatform repairs and essential
OL,9,Fstructural inspections.
OL,11,FMr Welford added: "By replacing
OL,12,Fessential infrastructure components,
OL,13,Fthis project ensures that a vital
OL,14,Fsection of the Metro system is future
OL,15,Fproofed and reliable for the long term.
OL,17,F"By scheduling these works during the
OL,18,FSpring half-term, we can avoid
OL,19,Fimpacting busy school commutes, and
OL,20,Fless congestion on the roads should
OL,21,Fspeed up alternative travel times.
