OL,6,F"It can only be carried out safely
OL,7,Fduring a five-day closure of the Metro
OL,8,Fsystem so that our engineers can get
OL,9,Fextended access to the lines."
OL,11,FCustomers are advised to plan ahead
OL,12,Fand allow extra time when travelling
OL,13,Fthrough the affected area.
